            <title>[FLINK-9934] Kafka table source factory produces invalid field mapping</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-9934</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;The Kafka table source factory produces an invalid field mapping when referencing a rowtime attribute from an input field. The check in &lt;tt&gt;TableSourceUtil#validateTableSource&lt;/tt&gt; therefore can fail.&lt;/p&gt;</description>
